Put your input active thing , after the if playing 


Something like this should work 



 module coherent-trigger-bot
def desc "Coherent Client's Trigger Bot"

on pre_tick if playing if target_entity :player,:armor_stand !if blocking if input_active left_control {
    if attack_progress >= 0.9 {
        if target_entity :player if blocking if hotbar_has #axe {
            switch #axe
            wait 0.05 switch back
        }
        input attack
    }
}